WEBVTT

00:00:28.960 --> 00:00:33.296
And another 50 percent
of those same young adults

00:00:33.320 --> 00:00:35.856
said that another major life goal

00:00:35.880 --> 00:00:37.720
was to become famous.

00:00:38.960 --> 00:00:40.176
(Laughter)

00:00:40.200 --> 00:00:46.856
And we're constantly told
to lean in to work, to push harder

00:00:46.880 --> 00:00:48.936
and achieve more.

00:00:48.960 --> 00:00:52.616
We're given the impression that these
are the things that we need to go after

00:00:52.640 --> 00:00:54.456
in order to have a good life.

00:00:54.480 --> 00:00:56.696
Pictures of entire lives,

00:00:56.720 --> 00:01:01.936
of the choices that people make
and how those choices work out for them,